Terrorist Briefing:
-------------------
We have taken some tourists as hostages, and are demanding 2 million dinnars for their release. But it looks like they sent in a SWAT task force instead, everyone get in position and don't let them free the hostages at all cost!


Counter-Terrorist Briefing:
----------------------------
We've been tipped off that a bunch of terrorists have taken some tourists as hostages, and are demanding a ransom for their release or they will all be killed. We have to act now in order to save each one of them, get in gear men and let's move out.
